0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:24:39.000Z","msg":"南韓女歌手SOMI（全昭彌）因奪下《Produce 101》冠軍而聲名大噪，去年更首度以solo女歌手身分出道，公司最新推出紀錄她高中畢業典禮的vlog，並曝光了她與王牌製作人Teddy的私下互動，然而最後一幕卻讓她登上熱搜，原來是她開著價值630萬台幣的名車，年紀輕輕引起討論！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4786/d4786274.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4786%2Fd4786274.jpg&h=824e75f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SOMI畢業典禮被弄哭。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／THEBLACKLABEL）<br />\n<br />\n在YouTube頻道「THEBLACKLABEL」公開《I AM SOMI》第一集的內容，聚焦在SOMI的高中畢業典禮，可以看到她與同學私下互動，其實就跟平常鏡頭前的她一模一樣，還多次被弄哭，個性十分自然可愛。<br />\n<br />\n畢業典禮後她回到所屬公司「 THE BLACK LABEL」吃炸醬麵，這是她離開JYP後簽約的新公司，由YG娛樂的王牌製作人Teddy所設立的，目前旗下知名藝人還有R&amp;B男歌手Zion.T。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4786/d4786275.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4786%2Fd4786275.jpg&h=4ee4756c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SOMI與Teddy相處不像老闆跟員工。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／THEBLACKLABEL）<br />\n<br />\n可能都是受過西洋教育，SOMI和Teddy不像一般老闆與員工般的拘謹關係，而是可以平起平做、大開玩笑，Teddy一見她就說「你怎麼在鏡頭前突然裝乖？」對方也說會這樣拿著鏡頭大方拍他的也只有SOMI，她甚至硬逼Teddy做「三行詩」，和老闆彷彿朋友般相處。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4786/d4786277.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4786%2Fd4786277.jpg&h=0cc17211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SOMI剛滿19歲坐駕駛座「我車升級了」登熱搜。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／THEBLACKLABEL）<br />\n<br />\n接著最後一幕的預告讓不少網友大吃一驚，SOMI坐在一台黃色轎車的駕駛座上，對著鏡頭大喊「我升級成黃色車了」，後面則坐著公司職員。網友大吃一驚，因為這台車是藍寶堅尼SUV，在韓要價2億5600萬，折合台幣大約為630萬。<br />\n<br />\n才剛滿19歲（南韓年紀則為20歲）的SOMI，曾在電視節目中說過想要換車，想換的就是畫面中這一款，雖然還不知道她只是試乘，還是車主，已引起網路討論，甚至讓「全昭彌」、「全昭彌 車」關鍵字登上韓網Naver熱搜。<br />\n<br />\n▼SOMI《I AM SOMI》第一集。（影片來源：YouTube THEBLACKLABEL）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yrGyOJv6Yo8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyrGyOJv6Yo8&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYqwDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=2702abd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yrGyOJv6Yo8</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:07:18.000Z","msg":"樓主借個位黎置頂可以嗎<br />\n<br />\n要人要錢要資源！線下文宣全港大行動 重建文宣網絡<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ausnGEU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ausnGEU</a>"},{"pid":"2289c1afb369f7f4ec3488154975994a3fd289bf","tid":1949040,"uid":203454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc6d37028149f8a39764c9b2a23252e527d4d871","tid":1949040,"uid":256952,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"27c788421d6451d59b0dce18e1f22427cb89b211","tid":1949040,"uid":74065,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"aef419f5d6e443fc28b06f6a30d6ac1a31dacf3a","tid":1949040,"uid":256952,"like":31,"dislike":8,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:31:02.000Z","msg":"應該係已經比社長 品嚐過"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"咁李秀滿係咪屌過邊伯賢"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CM9fgN3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCM9fgN3.jpg&h=8d0f54cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:11:40.000Z","msg":"邊妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138c2d88d03ccd54c253a684d82c30ef80c97050","tid":1949040,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:25:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">香港成為武漢2.0？成人隔離病床爆滿</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949209</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4a515fa109e9b07bb027f2e00c4f8cdf58c83bd8","tid":1949040,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b1df26e262f323b2d4b393b89c7ee51fbe5c4a0","tid":1949040,"uid":34444,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fc6d37028149f8a39764c9b2a23252e527d4d871","tid":1949040,"uid":256952,"like":5,"dislike":17,"sco